odml- Metadata handling for Matlab
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
Copyright (C) 2009-2011 Jan Grewe & Jan Benda
www.g-node.org/odml
Sources can be downloaded from github (www.github.com): git@github.com:G-Node/matlab-odml.git

odml is simple hierarchical format for storing and transfering metadata
about experimental data.
This library contains the Java implementation of it which can easily be used 
with Matlab.


